## Visualizing Trends in Firearm Purchases

The following chart depicts the number of FBI NCIS background checks performed each month from 2006 through May 2022. Whilst there is not a 1:1 correlation between background checks and firearm purchases, they are generally viewed as a reasonable approximate of such purchases.
![firearms sales](images/firearm_sales.jpg)

## Breaking Down Firearm Mortality by Intent

The treemap below shows a break down of firearm deaths by intent for the period 2001-2020. As is clear from from the diagram shown, the majority of deaths are a result of suicide rather than homicide.
